{
  "_meta": {
    "section": "dive-reports",
    "description": "Sample data for the Dive Reports section. Covers two features: DiveLogs (repeatable condition records per spot) and SpotRatings (one quality rating per user per spot).",
    "notes": [
      "DiveLogs are session-level records — visibility, current, optional notes and photos",
      "SpotRatings are location-level — one rating per userId+spotId, editable any time",
      "Rating is removed from DiveLog — it now lives exclusively in SpotRating",
      "spot-1 (Langøyene), spot-2 (Gressholmen), spot-4 (Ryvarden), spot-5 (Ålesund Dykkesenter) have logs",
      "log-1e has no notes and no photos — bare minimum log entry",
      "log-2a has photos to test thumbnail display",
      "user-1 is the currentUserId in DiveReportsProps — has ratings on spot-1 and spot-4"
    ],
    "relationships": {
      "DiveLog.spotId": "references DiveSpot.id in map-and-spots",
      "SpotRating.userId": "references User.id",
      "SpotRating.spotId": "references DiveSpot.id in map-and-spots",
      "one SpotRating per userId+spotId": "enforced at the application level"
    }
  },
